      "content": "but i literally can't take time off work right now to go back to the clinic. if i just use a bit of neosporin and a warm compress twice a day, is there any reason why that would actually make it worse? it's just a tiny bit of yellow fluid, it's not like it's a huge wound. surely it's fine to just treat it at home for a day or two and see if the redness goes down?",
